 philosophically offers particularly insightful means of understanding the nature of being in the world, thereby opening new paths for exploring how the self is constituted in its relation to the other.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Sep 2020) 0aSoccer coaches. 0aSoccer players. 0aSoccerxSocial aspects. 0aSportsxPhilosophy. 4aFIFA World Cup. 7aPHILOSOPHY / Movements / Critical Theory.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDUK eBook-Package 2019z978311069632540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9781478005551zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781478005551423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9781478005551.jpg  a978-3-11-069632-5  DUK eBook-Package 2019b2019  aEBA_DUK_ALL  aEBA_DUK_EALL  aEBA_DUK_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles